      <ul class="addtoany_list"><li><a class="a2a_dd addtoany_share_save" href="http://www.addtoany.com/share_save?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fveja.abril.com.br%2Fblog%2Freinaldo%2Fgeral%2Fmudei-um-pouco%2F&amp;linkname=Mudei%20um%20pouco"><img src="http://veja.abril.com.br/_estrutura/img/btn/wp-compartilhar.gif" alt="Share/Bookmark"/></a></li></ul>      <div class="barra-comentarios">
        
