 <div class="postConteudo"><p><a href="files/imagens/indio-bandeira-do-brasil-749574.jpg"><img style="FLOAT: right; MARGIN: 0px 0px 10px 10px; WIDTH: 149px; CURSOR: hand; HEIGHT: 99px" height="133" alt="" src="files/imagens/indio-bandeira-do-brasil-749571.jpg" width="149" border="0" /></a>
